{"hdf8dd66cg601cg43d6gae41gc4826c556580": ["If I'd known they were leaving, I would have given them an extra helping.", "1b35671b-e5d7-4943-bbd0-4c816b69b7cb", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_AD_ChefAndSon.html", "49251d4c-3d44-ea2c-6140-4b5d2a40619e"], "h391383fdgbb05g4960gb28agdfb68cd4d281": ["They're cowards, mother. You don't owe them anything.", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_AD_ChefAndSon.html", "317eed91-0fa2-2351-7bab-95741ddd54db"], "hc3f9b1e9g46c3g4e01g97d9gb32d0e2d5670": ["But can you really blame them? After Elturel...", "1b35671b-e5d7-4943-bbd0-4c816b69b7cb", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_AD_ChefAndSon.html", "77d00839-97ba-dc04-a62f-b327a6cf4142"], "hbd801f2dg4f25g4014g87f9g0042149d0cfd": ["We can't run forever. I'd rather stand and fight.", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_AD_ChefAndSon.html", "74ca44a6-fe1f-f0d4-9d55-87a7d7c527fd"], "hd112f519g9a83g4cc6gbd24ge399dbe4f21e": ["There's barely any rations left.", "1b35671b-e5d7-4943-bbd0-4c816b69b7cb", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_AD_ChefAndSon.html", "242cd42e-4f57-6b98-7de4-31dd952e8dba"], "h111c4c54gf9f2g48b7gae8ega942c84e099f": ["We'll make it last. We always do.", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_AD_ChefAndSon.html", "d3f4d3e9-06b8-531b-1a44-ccc91b32f561"], "h1d5055ddga885g49bcg83d3g13fc825ae826": ["I can't thin the broth much more than this.", "1b35671b-e5d7-4943-bbd0-4c816b69b7cb", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_AD_ChefAndSon.html", "b08190c3-540d-d2a7-70d9-c87f581441bb"], "h48e3323ag9e26g41c1g8523gfdc73b578195": ["It'll have to do.", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_AD_ChefAndSon.html", "2a3b5a8f-4690-0106-fe34-16098f77456c"]}